<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title></title>
        <link href="/css/_header.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="/css/_footer.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous">

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
        <script src="/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">
                <a href="/employees/dashboard"><img src="/images/logo.png"></a>
            </div>
            <input type="checkbox" id="click">
            <label for="click" class="menu-btn">
            <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
            </label>
            <ul>
               <li><a href="/employees/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
               <li><a href="/employees/profile">Profile</a></li>
               <li><a href="/employees/sign-out">Logout</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav><br><br>
        
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-5 text-danger" style="text-align: left;">Congratulations!!!</h1><hr>
            <p class="lead col-12" style="text-align: left;">We are pleased to inform you that you've successfully completed your onboarding process. For further Details, project team will contact you for project assignment and team manager. Your onboarding kit is on its way and you can check its details below:</p>
            <br>
                <div class="row" style="text-align: left;">
                    <div class="col-3"></div>
                    <div class="card col-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Onboarding Kit</h5><hr>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                1. Laptop <br>
                                2. Keyboard <br>
                                3. Mouse <br>
                                4. Headphone <br>
                                5. Security key <br>
                                6. T-shirt <br>
                                7. Stationary<br><hr>
                                Status : <%= records.kitStatus%>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div><div class="col-1"></div>
                </div><br>
            <p class="lead col-12" style="text-align: left;">It was really very nice knowing you and we are highly obliged for your coordination. As last step of this process, we would like to know your experience. For that purpose, kindly fill this Feedback Form.</p>
            <br>
            <a href="/employees/feedback_form" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-lg">Give Feedback</a>
            <br><br><hr><br>
            <h1 class="display-5 text-danger text-center">Thank You!!!</h1>

        </div><br><br>
    </body>
</html>